// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-0994 — Mass File Rename (handala)
// Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 3b3356b9-1274-5199-9997-2201cc82965a

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
